					<li outputclass="List 1"
  						class="- topic/li ">
						<p outputclass="List 1"
 							class="- topic/p ">(b)(1)(iv)  When the contracting officer determines through market research, that an article or suitable substitute is not available from a domestic source, the contracting officer must submit a <xref href="https://cs2.eis.af.mil/sites/10059/afcc/knowledge_center/templates/determination_and_findings_02.pdf"
    								scope="external"
    								format="pdf"
    								class="- topic/xref ">
								<u class="+ topic/ph hi-d/u ">Domestic Non-availability Determination (DNAD)</u>
							</xref>.  The DNAD must be submitted through the SCO to <xref href="mailto:usaf.pentagon.saf-aq.mbx.saf-aqc-workflow@mail.mil"
    								scope="external"
    								format="mailto"
    								class="- topic/xref ">
								<u class="+ topic/ph hi-d/u ">SAF/AQC</u>
							</xref> for approval by the Secretary of the Air Force (nondelegable).  See <ph outputclass="MP"
  								class="- topic/ph ">
								<xref outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
    									format="dita"
    									class="- topic/xref "
    									href="MP5325_7002-2.dita">MP5325.7002-2</xref>
							</ph>.</p>
